  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1145">
<l>kaḷittoṟuṅ kaḷḷuṇṭal vēṭṭaṟṟāṟ kāmam </l>
<l>veḷippaṭun tōṟu miṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As drinking liquor is delightful (to one) whenever one is in mirth, so is lust delightful to me whenever it is the subject of rumour.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
